## Task
Expand each beat into one or more screenplay scenes. The output should be a complete screenplay with:
- Proper scene headings (INT./EXT. LOCATION - TIME)
- Action lines describing what happens
- Character names in ALL CAPS before dialogue
- Centered dialogue blocks
- Parentheticals for delivery direction where needed
- Smooth transitions between scenes

